Frozen if at the top-left corner of an ice block.

Allows Yoshi to spit seeds 30 times.

Allows Yoshi to spit fire breath 3 times.

tooltipbase: Activates Kamek cutscene for the Raphael battle, then Raphael knocks Yoshi off-screen. The cutscene removes Yoshi's eggs and sends him to the screen exit of the screen above.

name: Goal ring
tooltipbase: Ends the level. Prevents horizontal scrolling after x+08 from its coordinates; requires a solid flat platform up to x+14.

name: GOAL text
tooltipbase: Floats in the top-right corner of the screen. Doesn't load its own graphics or palette.

tooltipbase: Falls from above to the top-center of the screen, then scrolls faster than layer 1, looping from one side of the screen to the other. Overwrites stripe slots 0-3 for the remainder of the sublevel.

tooltipbase: A large ghost that spits Shy Guys, if less than 6 eggs are present. Shrinks when hit, becoming stunned after 6 hits, but grows back over time.

tooltipbase: A glitched dynamic sprite that causes Yoshi to make a celebratory sound when collected, but doesn't actually give an inventory item.

name: Boss explosion
tooltipbase: A gray boss explosion that freezes Yoshi in place, then ends the level.

name: Key after x-8 boss
tooltipbase: A large key that freezes Yoshi in place, falls onto Yoshi's head, and ends the level.

name: Bigger Boo
tooltipbase: Boss activator.

name: Frog Pirate
tooltipbase: A frog that can grab Baby Mario with its tongue.

name: Fire breath
tooltipbase: Spawns for only 1 frame, but if overlapping an enemy, causes it to die as if by fire breath.
